and meet Mr. Miyagi.

27
00:04:34,733 --> 00:04:37,933
- I did. I said "hi."
- I want you to talk to him.

28
00:04:37,933 --> 00:04:39,533
You invited him here.
You talk to him.

29
00:04:39,533 --> 00:04:41,533
- What are you doing?
- Getting some meat.

30
00:04:41,533 --> 00:04:43,467
- Why?
- It's for a friend.

31
00:04:43,467 --> 00:04:45,667
May I ask which friend?

32
00:04:45,667 --> 00:04:49,867
Why is it, whenever I come back here,
I feel like I am in a police station.

33
00:04:49,867 --> 00:04:51,533
I am surprised you don't take
my fingerprints.

34
00:04:51,533 --> 00:04:55,267
I worry about you, that's all.
You have got to tell me what you want.

35
00:04:55,267 --> 00:04:58,067
What I want is for you
to leave me alone!

36
00:04:58,067 --> 00:05:00,333
Where are you going?
Susan!

37
00:05:03,267 --> 00:05:06,533
My name is Julie.
My mother's name was Susan.

38
00:05:06,533 --> 00:05:09,800
