86
00:09:58,933 --> 00:10:02,467
<i>Please do not leave
any baggage unattended.</i>

87
00:10:06,067 --> 00:10:09,467
- Skycap! Here.
- Yes, sir?

88
00:10:11,133 --> 00:10:13,267
I have tried sometimes...

89
00:10:13,267 --> 00:10:16,067
Just to talk to you
and not get angry...

90
00:10:16,067 --> 00:10:18,600
but everything gets messed up,
and I don't know why.

91
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,333
Things get messed up for me too.

92
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,533
Bye.

93
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:35,733
Grandmother barely on plane...

94
00:10:35,733 --> 00:10:37,667
miss you already.

95
00:10:39,467 --> 00:10:42,133
My birthday's in a couple of weeks.
I guess she forgot.

96
00:10:43,133 --> 00:10:45,067
Birthday.

97
00:10:45,067 --> 00:10:49,467
Very special day.
Everybody have birthday.

98
00:10:49,467 --> 00:10:53,800
Miyagi make you
special dinner, okay?

99
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:58,200
Tempura. Tempura, sukiyaki.
You like?

100
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,067
No like. Okay.

101
00:11:01,067 --> 00:11:04,267
Sushi.
Sushi, sashimi. Huh?

102
00:11:04,267 --> 00:11:06,667
Sashimi. No. Okay.

103
00:11:06,667 --> 00:11:12,333
Miyagi have it.
Hamburger teriyaki with French fry.

104
00:11:13,533 --> 00:11:17,800
Look, I don't need a special dinner.
I can take care of myself.

105
00:11:19,733 --> 00:11:22,067
- I know where I am going.
- Good.

106
00:11:22,067 --> 00:11:26,400
Miyagi know where you're going too.
Going school.

107
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:35,400
Miyagi pick you up here this afternoon.
Okay, Julie-san?

108
00:12:19,733 --> 00:12:22,000
Hey, get to class.
Get going.

109
00:12:24,267 --> 00:12:27,467
Get to class.
Let's go.

110
00:12:39,733 --> 00:12:43,867
Morning, Julie. No, no, no.
Those are bad for your ears.

111
00:12:43,867 --> 00:12:45,267
Go to hell, Ned.

112
00:12:45,933 --> 00:12:48,333
Now, I could take you down
to the principal's office...

113
00:12:48,333 --> 00:12:50,333
....and get you into a little trouble.

114
00:12:50,333 --> 00:12:54,333
Or, I could pick you up tomorrow night
and take you down to the docks.

115
00:12:54,333 --> 00:12:58,067
You have been to the docks, haven't you,
Julie? Pretty girl like you.

116
00:12:58,067 --> 00:12:59,800
Dream on.

117
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:05,200
Hey! Most girls in this school
invite me.

118
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,867
Now, you're lucky
to get an invitation.

119
00:13:07,867 --> 00:13:10,800
Now, come on, Julie.
You know it's going to happen.

120
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:12,400
Let go of me!

121
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:14,933
Start hanging out
with me and my friends...

122
00:13:14,933 --> 00:13:18,000
