that you want.

123
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,133
- Let go of me.
- What's going on, Ned?

124
00:13:20,133 --> 00:13:22,333
Colonel Dugan, sir.

125
00:13:22,333 --> 00:13:24,533
I caught this young lady
smoking cigarettes.

126
00:13:24,533 --> 00:13:26,667
What are you talking about?
I wasn't smoking.

127
00:13:26,667 --> 00:13:30,533
Her name is Julie Pierce, sir.

128
00:13:32,133 --> 00:13:34,600
To the office. Let's go.

129
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,533
Curb your dog.

130
